+`CONTEXT-MAP.md` exists at the root, the profile has multiple contexts. The map points to where each one lives:
 
 ```
 /
 ├── CONTEXT-MAP.md
+├── CONTEXT.md                        ← profile-wide glossary
 ├── docs/
 │   └── adr/                          ← system-wide decisions
-├── src/
-│   ├── ordering/
+├── <path-to-project>/
+│   ├── <project-a>/
 │   │   ├── CONTEXT.md
